<p><strong>Step-by-step instructions</strong></p>
<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>Step 1
{: .label .label-step}
Do this thing
{: .step}

Step 2
{: .label .label-step}
